{"tid":1631743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢夢到藍絲的士狗開車撞人！有嘢要提醒！","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:12:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:56:49.000Z","uid":195403,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0a28d996aab75049d1d8f097e391cf719f449492","tid":1631743,"uid":195403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:12:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/07/000958_0ef340288b8684f605ab5058b6327fa8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F07%2F000958_0ef340288b8684f605ab5058b6327fa8.png&h=078ea741&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/07/001008_25ca435cde0368c6dc3d0356c919f69a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F07%2F001008_25ca435cde0368c6dc3d0356c919f69a.png&h=2b58cd32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n先講明 我係借朋友account開Po<br />\n<br />\n首先好欣賞大家最後獅鳥咗條死廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係有一樣嘢大家必須要注意！！！<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">先可以減少有手足受傷嘅機會</span></strong><br />\n當時夢見到架的士最初係停左嘅 好多人圍住 跟著就有位手足過去打佢架車同玻璃。而門係開到嘅。<br />\n<br />\n大家要注意嘅係 條藍絲廢老仲係車入面 佢仲可以隨時不停開車撞人。所以 既然門係開到 必須先拉佢落車 先可以確保到大家唔會受傷。而且大家圍埋去時 唔好圍太迫 因為好多人會走都走唔到 同埋真係唔好企喺車頭 近嘅企車身 遠嘅就自己醒啲 去啲佢撞唔到你嘅位<br />\n<br />\n我借人account開Po唔係想屌個位手足衝動 只係想提下大家 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">要拉咗人落車先再獅鳥</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"0b964cfb8869cd6cada77a34f51c74f31e7ae154","tid":1631743,"uid":195403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:18:34.000Z","msg":"不割蓆！不篤灰！不分化！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0786d906497c898e914f3fc81db28eb5bec8e3eb","tid":1631743,"uid":19